// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// 🏛️  DESIGNS OF DREAMS — Unified Database Schema
// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// Shared across: Dashboard (Admin) + dodshop (Customer Website)
// Database:      PostgreSQL
// ORM:           Prisma v7
// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

datasource db {
  provider = "postgresql"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}

generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// ENUMERATIONS
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

enum AdminRole {
  SUPER_ADMIN
  MANAGER
}

enum AccountStatus {
  ACTIVE
  INACTIVE
}

enum ProductStatus {
  DRAFT
  ACTIVE
  ARCHIVED
}

enum OrderStatus {
  PENDING
  PROCESSING
  PACKED
  SHIPPED
  DELIVERED
  CANCELLED
  RETURNED
  REFUNDED
}

enum PaymentStatus {
  UNPAID
  PAID
  REFUND_INITIATED
  REFUNDED
}

enum PaymentMethod {
  CREDIT_CARD
  DEBIT_CARD
  UPI
  NET_BANKING
  BANK_TRANSFER
  COD
}

enum InventoryLogType {
  STOCK_IN
  SALE
  RETURN
  MANUAL_ADJUST
}

enum ContactStatus {
  UNREAD
  REPLIED
  ARCHIVED
}

enum ReturnStatus {
  PENDING
  APPROVED
  REJECTED
  PICKED_UP
  REFUNDED
}

enum AuditStatus {
  SUCCESS
  FAILED
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 1. ADMIN USER — Dashboard administrator accounts
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model AdminUser {
  id           String        @id @default(uuid())
  name         String
  email        String        @unique
  passwordHash String
  role         AdminRole     @default(MANAGER)
  avatar       String?
  status       AccountStatus @default(ACTIVE)
  lastLogin    DateTime?
  createdAt    DateTime      @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime      @updatedAt

  @@map("admin_users")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 2. CATEGORY — Product categories (Sarees, Kurtis, etc.)
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Category {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  name        String   @unique
  slug        String   @unique
  description String?  @db.Text
  image       String?
  sortOrder   Int      @default(0)
  isActive    Boolean  @default(true)
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt

  products Product[]

  @@map("categories")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 3. COLLECTION — Seasonal/themed collections
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Collection {
  id          String    @id @default(uuid())
  name        String    @unique
  slug        String    @unique
  description String?   @db.Text
  image       String?
  season      String?
  isActive    Boolean   @default(true)
  startDate   DateTime?
  endDate     DateTime?
  createdAt   DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime  @updatedAt

  products Product[]

  @@map("collections")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 4. PRODUCT — Full product catalog
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Product {
  id            String        @id @default(uuid())
  name          String
  slug          String        @unique
  sku           String        @unique
  categoryId    String
  category      Category      @relation(fields: [categoryId], references: [id])
  subCategory   String
  collectionId  String?
  collection    Collection?   @relation(fields: [collectionId], references: [id])
  mrp           Float
  sellingPrice  Float
  discount      Float         @default(0)
  gst           Float         @default(5)
  stock         Int           @default(0)
  lowStockAlert Int           @default(2)
  description   String        @db.Text
  fabric        String
  weaveType     String
  occasion      String
  sareeLength      String?
  blousePiece      String?
  careInstructions String?
  origin           String?
  colors        String[]
  sizes         String[]
  features      String[]
  tags          String[]
  status        ProductStatus @default(ACTIVE)
  featured      Boolean       @default(false)
  bestSeller    Boolean       @default(false)
  premium       Boolean       @default(true)
  newArrival    Boolean       @default(false)
  images        String[]
  videoUrl      String?
  rating        Float         @default(0)
  reviewCount   Int           @default(0)
  createdAt     DateTime      @default(now())
  updatedAt     DateTime      @updatedAt

  inventoryLogs InventoryLog[]
  orderItems    OrderItem[]
  cartItems     CartItem[]
  wishlistItems WishlistItem[]

  @@map("products")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 5. CUSTOMER — Website registered customers
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Customer {
  id           String   @id @default(uuid())
  name         String
  email        String   @unique
  passwordHash String
  phone        String?
  avatar       String?
  notes        String?  @db.Text
  isVerified   Boolean  @default(false)
  joinedDate   DateTime @default(now())
  createdAt    DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime @updatedAt

  addresses     Address[]
  cartItems     CartItem[]
  wishlistItems WishlistItem[]
  orders        Order[]
  returnRequests ReturnRequest[]

  @@map("customers")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 6. ADDRESS — Customer shipping/billing addresses
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Address {
  id         String  @id @default(uuid())
  customerId String
  customer   Customer @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  label      String   @default("Home")
  line1      String
  line2      String?
  city       String
  state      String
  postalCode String
  country    String   @default("India")
  phone      String?
  isDefault  Boolean  @default(false)

  @@map("addresses")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 7. CART ITEM — Customer shopping cart
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model CartItem {
  id         String   @id @default(uuid())
  customerId String
  customer   Customer @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  productId  String
  product    Product  @relation(fields: [productId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  quantity   Int      @default(1)
  size       String
  createdAt  DateTime @default(now())

  @@unique([customerId, productId, size])
  @@map("cart_items")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 8. WISHLIST ITEM — Customer wishlist
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model WishlistItem {
  id         String   @id @default(uuid())
  customerId String
  customer   Customer @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  productId  String
  product    Product  @relation(fields: [productId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  createdAt  DateTime @default(now())

  @@unique([customerId, productId])
  @@map("wishlist_items")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 9. ORDER — Order headers
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Order {
  id              String        @id // Format: DOD-XXXXXX
  customerId      String
  customer        Customer      @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id])
  customerName    String
  customerEmail   String
  totalAmount     Float
  discountAmount  Float         @default(0)
  gstAmount       Float         @default(0)
  shippingAmount  Float         @default(0)
  grandTotal      Float
  status          OrderStatus   @default(PENDING)
  paymentStatus   PaymentStatus @default(UNPAID)
  paymentMethod   PaymentMethod
  shippingAddress Json          // { line1, line2, city, state, postalCode, country, phone }
  trackingDetails Json?         // { carrier, trackingId, estimatedDelivery, logs[] }
  cancelReason    String?       @db.Text
  returnReason    String?       @db.Text
  couponCode      String?
  createdAt       DateTime      @default(now())
  updatedAt       DateTime      @updatedAt

  items          OrderItem[]
  returnRequests ReturnRequest[]

  @@map("orders")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 10. ORDER ITEM — Individual items within orders
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model OrderItem {
  id        String  @id @default(uuid())
  orderId   String
  order     Order   @relation(fields: [orderId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  productId String
  product   Product @relation(fields: [productId], references: [id])
  name      String
  sku       String
  price     Float
  quantity  Int
  size      String
  color     String?
  image     String

  @@map("order_items")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 11. INVENTORY LOG — Stock movement tracking
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model InventoryLog {
  id          String           @id @default(uuid())
  productId   String
  product     Product          @relation(fields: [productId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  productName String
  sku         String
  change      Int              // + for stock in, - for stock out
  type        InventoryLogType
  timestamp   DateTime         @default(now())
  user        String           // Name and Role of the actor

  @@map("inventory_logs")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 12. RETURN REQUEST — Return/refund lifecycle tracking
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model ReturnRequest {
  id              String       @id @default(uuid())
  orderId         String
  order           Order        @relation(fields: [orderId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  customerId      String
  customer        Customer     @relation(fields: [customerId], references: [id])
  reason          String
  description     String?      @db.Text
  images          String[]
  status          ReturnStatus @default(PENDING)
  refundAmount    Float?
  rejectionReason String?      @db.Text
  createdAt       DateTime     @default(now())
  resolvedAt      DateTime?

  @@map("return_requests")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 13. CONTACT FORM — Customer contact submissions
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model ContactForm {
  id        String        @id @default(uuid())
  name      String
  email     String
  phone     String?
  subject   String
  message   String        @db.Text
  status    ContactStatus @default(UNREAD)
  reply     String?       @db.Text
  repliedAt DateTime?
  createdAt DateTime      @default(now())

  @@map("contact_forms")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 14. CMS CONFIG — Homepage CMS configuration (singleton)
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model CMSConfig {
  id                  String   @id @default("singleton")
  heroTitle           String
  heroSubtitle        String
  heroImage           String
  announcementText    String?
  announcementLink    String?
  announcementActive  Boolean  @default(true)
  featuredCollections Json     // [{ id, name, image, count }]
  gallery             Json?
  bannerMiddle        String?
  footerBio           String?  @db.Text
  seoTitle            String
  seoDescription      String   @db.Text
  updatedAt           DateTime @updatedAt

  @@map("cms_config")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 15. COUPON — Promotional discount codes
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Coupon {
  id              String   @id @default(uuid())
  code            String   @unique
  discountPercent Float
  maxDiscount     Float?
  minOrderValue   Float    @default(0)
  usageLimit      Int?
  timesUsed       Int      @default(0)
  isActive        Boolean  @default(true)
  validFrom       DateTime @default(now())
  validUntil      DateTime?
  createdAt       DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt       DateTime @updatedAt

  @@map("coupons")
}

// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// 16. SECURITY LOG — Admin activity audit trail
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model SecurityLog {
  id        String      @id @default(uuid())
  timestamp DateTime    @default(now())
  action    String
  adminName String
  role      String
  ip        String?
  device    String?
  status    AuditStatus

  @@map("security_logs")
}
